Author: vitaminsplz
Text: Hey it'll be ok!  I actually talked to my chem teacher when i ieot doing less-than-desirable/expected even though i felt like i had all the conceots down. He told me that even he had the same problem and that it took him a while to get into the mindset necessary for chem. Chemistry is more than just memorizing and applying -- it requires a sonewhat different thought process  Idk if that'll be reassuring to you or kot, but it helped me so thought i'd share
